</a>，当时她举着一个标语牌，参考了该乐队标志性的“What&#39;s My Age Again”视频。</p><p>这场期待已久的演出将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182-reunite-with-tom-delonge-announce-new-music-and-world-tour-buy-tickets-3326660">汤姆·德隆格回归阵容</a>后三人组在英国和爱尔兰的首次演出。目前尚不清楚受影响音乐会的重新安排巡演日期何时公布，但由于乐队尚未向持票人提供任何退款细节，这些日期似乎应该尽快公布。</p><p>十月即将在英国举行的所有音乐会——包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blink-182-add-second-london-show-to-2023-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3329247">伦敦 O2 体育场连续两晚的音乐会</a>——都将按计划举行。 </p><figure id="attachment_3457186" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3457186" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3457186" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="考特尼·卡戴珊和特拉维斯·巴克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Kourtney-Kardashian-Travis-Barker-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3457186" class="wp-caption-text">考特尼·卡戴珊和特拉维斯·巴克。图片来源：Jeff Bottari/Zuffa LLC，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>在主唱透露他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-delonge-says-new-blink-182-album-is-only-weeks-away-3488828">即将发行的专辑“只剩下几周（几天）”</a>之后，英国和爱尔兰的日期被推迟。目前，该唱片的确切发行日期尚未公布，尽管德隆格最近确实告诉歌迷，即将推出的项目将 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-delonge-blink-182-new-album-probably-our-best-3473791">成为他们迄今为止“最好的专辑”</a> 。</p><p>乐队剩余的英国巡演日期如下：</p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>11 伦敦 O2</strong><br /> <strong>12 伦敦 O2</strong><br /> <strong>14 伯明翰公用事业竞技场</strong><br /><strong>15 曼彻斯特 AO 竞技场</strong><br /><strong>16 曼彻斯特 AO 竞技场</strong></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-barker-shares-update-after-life-threatening-emergency-that-postponed-blink-182-dates-3494224">特拉维斯·巴克 (Travis Barker) 在“危及生命的紧急情况”后分享了推迟 Blink-182 日期的最新消息，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
